Package com.turvo.abcbanking.repository

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BaseRepository<T,I extends java.io.Serializable>
    Generic base repository contract/interface to cater DB operations for multiple system entities This contract inserts a layer of abstraction between database used and system entity repositories Current solution is based on SQL database that's why extended CrudRepository for basic operation currently.
    BranchRepository
    Standard repository class for Branch operations
    CounterRepository
    Standard repository class for Counter operations
    CounterXServiceStepRepository
    Standard repository class for Counter Service Step mapping operations
    CustomerRepository
    Standard repository class for Customer operations
    RoleRepository
    Standard repository class for Role operations
    ServiceRepository
    Standard repository class for Service operations
    ServiceRepositoryCustom
    Custom repository class for Service operations
    ServiceStepRepository
    Standard repository class for Service Step operations
    ServiceXServiceStepRepository
    Standard repository class for Service and Service Step relationship operations
    TokenRepository
    Standard repository class for Token operations
    TokenRepositoryCustom
    Custom repository class for Token operations
    TokenWorkflowRepository
    Standard repository class for Token Workflow operations
    UserRepository
    Standard repository class for User operations
    UserXRoleRepository
    Standard repository class for UserXRole operations
